urce=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false |publisher=Gorgias Press LLC |isbn=978-1-59333-115-3 |ref=harv |accessdate=2011-11-04}} *{{Cite book |last=van Donzel |first=E. J. |year=1994 |title=Islamic desk reference |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zHxsWspxGIIC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false |publisher=Brill |isbn=978-90-04-09738-4 |ref=harv |accessdate=2011-11-04}} {{refend}}
